<title>SING THE LOVE OF JESUS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Sauin la'n sauin thusim lui,
 Hukdampa hehpihna chu;
 Isu A lopina la'n sau,
 Chunglama tatsa haw tawh.

[V2]
 Isu hehpihna la'n sauin,
 Pakla gamtin ah gi hen;
 Thusim maktak chu la'n sauin,
 Khawvel pumin a hetman.

[V3]
 2. Lungsiet na lul chuh la'n sauin,
 Isu thih zie la'n sauin;
 Na lasak un namtin hip hen,
 Tanpa deihum kawm achun.

[V4]
 3. Tatsa te'n thusim chuh la'n sau,
 Sau inla sa nawn zelun;
 Gamtin apat a mipite'n,
 La ei sakpih macheng un.</lyrics>
</song>